1. In order to be able to build and test project with Jenkins it is necessary to set next environment
variables:
- ANDROID_HOME and ANDROID_NDK_HOME
both of them can be set in the "/etc/environment" file (sudo gedit /etc/environment)
Example:
ANDROID_NDK_HOME=/home/user/Software/android-ndk
ANDROID_HOME=/home/user/Software/android-studio/sdk
Note that it is necessary to LogOut / LogIn form the users account in order to force the changes

2. RootTools

